# Procedure to execute 
# The folder contains two python files lsh.py and driver.py

1.	Run driver.py file using 'python driver.py'
2.	Enter the query
3.	Enter if you want to build the model again or load pre-built model
4.	Similar DNA sequences will be retrieved
